title: We'll Trend It Live! 4/20: Winning Time, A$AP Rocky, Movie Season, Piers Morgan & Snickers
itunes:title: We'll Trend It Live! 4/20: Winning Time, A$AP Rocky, Movie Season, Piers Morgan & Snickers
description:
In this edition of Trends, Jack and Miles discuss 4/20, Jerry West's reaction to Winning Time, A$AP Rocky's arrest, the influx of theater-worthy movies, Piers Morgan's upcoming 'explosive' interview with Donald Trump and a viral photo of a smooth Snickers bar.
